    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy her. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed, and treated like a member of the family. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape; you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish on her. She drives just as smoothly as the day she rolled off the lot. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and looked after by a true car nut, you\u2019ve found it. Come by for a chat and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
